            <svg class="w-icon"><use href="#i-zap"/></svg> Why we exist
          </span>
          <h2 class="abw__title w-reveal">AI broke the old proof. We rebuilt it.</h2>
          <p class="abw__body w-reveal">For decades, B2B selling ran on claims &mdash; decks, demos, promises. Then AI made claims free and infinite, and buyers stopped believing them. What survived was the oldest signal there is: a peer who's actually done it. The problem was never a shortage of happy customers; it was that their proof never reached the right buyer in time. SlashExperts exists to close that gap &mdash; to make customer proof a system, delivered proactively by Carly and on demand through Experts+.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

